After all other work and logging, the VERY LAST line of your output MUST be exactly one of:
- `ROUTINE_COMPLETE` — every step finished, nothing skipped/blocked/partial.
- `ROUTINE_INCOMPLETE: <one-line reason>` — anything was skipped, blocked, deferred, or failed.

Output nothing after that line. This line is how Steve gets a done / not-fully-done alert on Telegram.
